                &lt;li&gt;(Key) city - (Value) Customer's city.&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;(Key) state/province - (Value) Customer's state/ province.&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;(Key) telephone - (Value) Phone number of the customer.&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;(Key) country - (Value) Customer's country. Two character country code, see
